Class ObservableSupplier

  • java.lang.Object

        • ChildCareTech.services.ObservableDTOs.ObservableSupplier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ObservablePersonInterface<SupplierDTO>, java.io.Serializable

    public class ObservableSupplier
extends SupplierDTO
implements ObservablePersonInterface<SupplierDTO>
    This class provides a wrapper for the SupplierDTO class. The purpose is to simplify SupplierDTO instances' display in tables.
